title: FSX / FSX SE Skyaitraffic Installer with SP1
description: SkyAITraffic which is a freeware traffic program that has been sabotaged by Avsim was taken down from the net. But it lives on here! It is simply the best AItraffic program on the market today and sadly the community was robbed of it. To install, simply run the installer, go to the folder it created, and copy over the traffic files to your FSX or FSX Steam. Read the manual as well
